<view class="card">
  <view class="team-banner">📌 {{teamName || '未知队伍'}}</view>

  <view class="form-item">
    <text class="form-label">当前阶段</text>
    <picker mode="selector" range="{{stages}}" value="{{stageIndex}}" bindchange="onStageChange">
      <view class="picker-val">{{stages[stageIndex]}} ▾</view>
    </picker>
  </view>

  <view class="form-item">
    <text class="form-label">✅ 本次完成的里程碑</text>
    <input
      class="form-input"
      placeholder="如：NEMU 成功运行 hello world"
      value="{{milestone}}"
      bindinput="onInput"
      data-field="milestone"
      maxlength="60"
    />
  </view>

  <view class="form-item">
    <text class="form-label">📝 详细内容</text>
    <textarea
      class="form-textarea"
      placeholder="今天做了什么？遇到了什么问题？怎么解决的？"
      value="{{content}}"
      bindinput="onInput"
      data-field="content"
      maxlength="500"
    />
  </view>

  <view class="form-item">
    <text class="form-label">🚧 目前卡在哪里（选填）</text>
    <input
      class="form-input"
      placeholder="如：不理解 NEMU 的内存寻址机制"
      value="{{blockedBy}}"
      bindinput="onInput"
      data-field="blockedBy"
      maxlength="100"
    />
  </view>

  <button
    class="btn btn-primary"
    style="margin-top: 8rpx;"
    bindtap="onSubmit"
    loading="{{submitting}}"
    disabled="{{submitting}}"
  >
    提交打卡
  </button>
</view>

<view class="tip card">
  <text class="tip-title">💡 好的打卡示例</text>
  <text class="tip-text">「PA1.1 完成，NEMU 成功运行 hello world，截图附上；目前卡在 x86 内存寻址的段机制，还没理解段基地址如何与 GDT 关联」</text>
</view>
